{"tid":2253039,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【LOGIC】認同《環球時報》無考取內地記者證既付國豪係「假記者」＝認同警方既政府認證記者制度","createTime":"2020-10-22T01:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T03:22:08.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54fda79ba43c085879e70b087fd54ea56f96215d","tid":2253039,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:47:14.000Z","msg":"不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n汁：<br />\n<br />\n環球時報員工付蟈蠔親口承認自己係假記者 ： 沒有於內地考取記者證<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2252919\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2252919</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港警方周二（9月22日）向香港四個傳媒組織致函，表示將修改《警察通例》中的「傳媒代表」定義，拒絶承認記者協會（記協）等媒體工作者工會的記者證，作為辨識記者的方法。<br />\n<br />\n新規定下，警方只承認已登記香港政府新聞處發佈系統的傳媒機構和國際認可的非本地媒體，多家香港及國際網媒、學生媒體和自由記者均會受到影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-54261148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-54261148&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPTJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=33995bdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-54261148&h=0c997806\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-54261148</a>"},{"pid":"5269142b75e47f288b384ebbc9a07bfd397c669a","tid":2253039,"uid":134323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:51:10.000Z","msg":"我理撚得你有無大陸記者證<br />\n無記協記者証咪唔係記者"},{"pid":"693cb55a6662170b64e8457ab551c6e75ad7f3e7","tid":2253039,"uid":35113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T01:52:52.000Z","msg":"判斷佢係咪假記者，係睇佢當時喺現場嘅行為符唔符合記者嘅角色<br />\n如果佢根本唔係履行緊記者嘅職責，咁話佢扮記者有咩問題<br />\n根本唔關記者證事"},{"pid":"82daa2045131cdddc80e74ea2c2f29f576030385","tid":2253039,"uid":253119,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"693cb55a6662170b64e8457ab551c6e75ad7f3e7","tid":2253039,"uid":35113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl